Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:21.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}掌上的微风 在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:35.21,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}我已经能用全新的笑容 向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:47.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}尽管回忆溢满心头 我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:57.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无所谓在干掉的泪痕中 有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:01.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:10.03,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}没错 我会以迎接朋友的方式 温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.79,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:23.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头 我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:27.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员到底怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两三天来都没有露脸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#18 响子的礼物 咦!这个要送给我?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是房租
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是伙食费
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,如果是吃 “站着吃荞麦面”解决的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来,生活费支出应该是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这些应该就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要参加茶茶丸的派对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要去参加派对啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰教练说他要来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然管理员也会来罗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬你美丽的瞳眸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这么说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话,你也会来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五点开始喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下2488圆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么够呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆不要送礼物…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够公然送礼物的 只有圣诞节而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便宜也没关系 最重要的是诚意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,今天就去买
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,管理员到底是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来…来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很吵耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 至少让我看一下背影会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,小津江啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天?好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚好要出去买东西 买完后再跟你见面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大婶 不要这样光明正大偷听好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是女朋友打来的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用从二楼奋力冲下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话又不会跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话是不会跑掉没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话是不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见管理员的话 就去敲她的门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没什么事找她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个藉口不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要稍微学习一下 三鹰教练的厚脸皮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾,我天生害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是没志气而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,居然说我没志气?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就让你看看我的志气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出门了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也只有声音而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好花了两千圆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天又要过苦日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了,船到桥头自然直
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,这样就有理由 去敲管理员的门了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要送给我?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以打开来看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好漂亮的耳环
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又在撞电线杆了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底在干什么啊? 真是个怪胎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得改改我的幻想症才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的额头怎么了?流血了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,我拿手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,我用自己的手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我一杯美式咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天找我有什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然早了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然织得不太好 不过是我亲手织的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴戴看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有把小津江的份算进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,既然已经收了人家的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是得…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要送给我的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以打开来看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:10:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,是耳环
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好成熟喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会…会吗?你戴起来很好看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,我真的好高兴喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你这么高兴,我也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,我是白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种优柔寡断的个性 难道到死也改不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,我真的好高兴喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小津江真的好可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然高兴成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是只有声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,真的好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这三天来是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忙着编织围巾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说,这是要送给我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你喜不喜欢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当…当然喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先失陪了,我想去补个眠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为连续熬夜都没睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你熬夜织围巾?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的围巾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,我好高兴喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有礼物可以送管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今把房租拿出来用…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.79,0:14:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,不可以用房租
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房租付不出来 反而会给管理员添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,伙食费…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是四、五天不吃 应该死不了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:14:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总不能叫她还我吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.89,0:15:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,我真的好高兴喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,我真的好高兴喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员送了一条围巾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且听说是熬夜三天亲手织的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用上好的毛线耶 围起来很温暖喔,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看,让我也围围看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要这样拉啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,这是我的宝贝围巾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么态度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你也过来喝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年终大扫除,现在还太早啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟你说过不要拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在在找东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了,请不要吵我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪了 我记得放在这个抽屉里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?五代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到一张准考证
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怀念喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经过了一年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重考生时代真的很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片也一脸苦恼的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼神黯然无光 一付闹别扭的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然会变得灰暗!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那时候被你们当作白痴耍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也一样被当作白痴耍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身分没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是一刻馆的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之东西找到了,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是!我要找的不是那个!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,你也回自己的房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会趁你睡觉时侵犯你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种你就试试看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然睡得这么安心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到一百圆!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴,一百圆能干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么睡相嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要送给我?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思没有包装起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里,别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的别针
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这个别针吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛好像很红
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我昨晚熬夜没睡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会睡到傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得好饱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条围巾好温暖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,跟帽子也很合喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你戴这个别针也很好看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还适合这么可爱的东西吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么话,你明明还很年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是,我也才22岁而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,22岁?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大我两岁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才大我两岁而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该不会造成结婚的障碍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才差两岁而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代也要去茶茶丸的派对?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正好,一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,想不到你蛮怕冷的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明这么年轻…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:21:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,这条围巾好温暖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是管理员用真心亲手织的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,这是音无小姐亲手织的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该,看你能说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无小姐亲手织的围巾 真的很温暖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,织同样的围巾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我只有这点本事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颜色织得不同 这点你实在太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.40,0:21:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果以为自己特别 就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 送同样的围巾是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:22:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是脚踏两条船?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是我跟五代是同等级的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我究竟哪里做的不好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的围巾,好温暖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的用心真的好温暖 让我打从心里暖和起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.11,0:22:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个披肩好温暖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.78,0:22:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为上次我脚扭伤 受到大家的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一点心意兼圣诞节礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.02,0:22:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我爸爸 管理员都帮他织了一条围巾喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.03,0:22:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一家三口都有比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:23:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老公高兴到 连眼泪都流出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的围巾花样都一样耶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,因为时间不够 所以大家都织一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说,就算花样一样 但是颜色不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,也帮我织一条吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.84,0:23:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.53,0:23:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三更半夜的一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一片寂静之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一对男女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.33,0:23:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得哪来的钟声响个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.33,0:23:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“五代和响子! 俩人的夜晚充满危险”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办? 希望不会有事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.63,0:24:06.63,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.17,0:24:34.52,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}那天在陌生的城市下了一场阵雨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.55,0:24:41.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}你非常在意淋湿的高跟鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.27,0:24:49.45,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}从前你用那隐藏着 稚气的侧脸和我交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.48,0:24:55.54,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}你说的话语至今仍能想起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.57,0:25:03.34,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}一开始就仿佛 置身电影中的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.37,0:25:12.02,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}你轻声细语地说着 安静的最后一幕

